Titolo: Hind (video game)

Anno: 1996

Descrizione: Hind is a computer game released by Digital Integration in 1996 for DOS and Windows 95. It is the successor to Apache Longbow.
The game is a combat flight simulator which features the Soviet military Mi-24V Hind-E helicopter. The original versions came with a detailed 99 page printed manual explaining the basics of helicopter flight and control, along with the specific traits of the Mi-24 helicopter and its weaponry.